x^2 - y^2 = z^3
x=(n+1)(n+2)/2
y=n(n+1)/2
z=(n+1)
n \in \mathbb{N}
\{(m+t)^2 - (m-t)^2 \}(4mt)^2 = (4mt)^3
x=4mt(m+t)
y=4mt|m-t|
z=4mt
m,t\in \mathbb{N}
z = a^m b^n
m,n \geq 1
x+y = a^k b^l
x-y = a^{3m-k} b^{3n-l}
1 \leq k <3m
1 \leq l <3n
z = a_1^{m_1} a_2^{m_2} \cdots a_k^{m_k}
x = \dfrac{a^kb^l + a^{3m-k} b^{3n-l}}2 \text{ and }y = \dfrac{a^kb^l - a^{3m-k} b^{3n-l}}2
